{"tid":828674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生苦短，過左今次山竹襲港，會對自己好D","createTime":"2018-09-20T00:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T04:29:14.000Z","uid":43327,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ef7505a947370affbc5d43da107abd75a96d04","tid":828674,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"個風黎香港之前都深知仆街，留響屋企<br />\n但屋企明明大大棟石矢樓，比風吹都搖到仆街<br />\n幾驚棟樓冧左，咁就冇左條命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前死慳死抵，一個月所有開支壓縮到 $2000 蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成份人工儲起來，諗住留返D錢留返來將來應急用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來買左樓，樓都唔一定係安樂窩黎，一唔小心就<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人在天堂，錢在銀行</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人生苦短，及時行樂</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：A0、青頭仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 決定以後每日 M 記加大！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310e45891a8e125750dfa5b7a5513585d51da514","tid":828674,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"入銀行做咪可以人同銀都係銀行"},{"pid":"578e2c3dc375c457e1808104c626ddda6a4a3321","tid":828674,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310e45891a8e125750dfa5b7a5513585d51da514","tid":828674,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"入銀行做咪可以人同銀都係銀行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:29:14.000Z","msg":"邊有咁好福氣做到死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}